      "layout": "The site uses a max-width contained layout generally, but a full-bleed hero section is often employed, characterized by a dark background with a large, centered, high-contrast headline. Section rhythm varies but includes distinct alternating bands of color (e.g., dark with light text, then light with dark text). Content is often arranged in prominent centered stacks for headlines and quotes, with occasional two-column layouts for information blocks. There is a prominent sticky top navigation bar. The overall density is comfortable, with generous vertical spacing between major sections, letting dramatic headlines breathe.",
